<c74object category='controller, data' name='recall.shift' module='max, recall'>
  <digest>
    Recall and shift a data stream for live performance.
  </digest>
  <!--DESCRIPTION-->
  <description>
    <o>recall.shift</o> samples N positions of a data stream input that may be recalled and played back with varying offsets.
    Args:
    first arg (opt) #1 is the name of the array
attributes:
@range: random range (def. 1000)
@scale_low: scaled output, low output value (def. 0)
@scale_high: scaled output, high output value (def. 1000, matches range)
@loop: turn random recall on/off
@recallDuration: how many data points to recall (def. 8th note, four values)
@recallIndexStart: where to recall data from (def. first value)
@scaleOutput: gates 2nd outlet, the scaled output values.
  </description>
